Setting up the Selenium IDE to run the tests requires 2 plugins;
First, it requires an ide plugin that supports looping:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11033321/how-to-loop-tests-in-selenium-ide
and the implicit wait plugin;
https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/selenium-ide-implicit-wait/

After restarting the IDE, load in the attached volume-loop test case, select the "hour glass" to activate the waiting plugin, then ensure the console is logged in and sitting on the volumes landing page, now run the test.
